Defendant in custody.   
Defendant is before the Court for sentencing, his probation having been revoked effective 07-28-15.  
Defendant is sentenced to the Wisconsin State Prison System for a total sentence of five (5) years.   Two (2) years initial confinement, followed by three (3) years extended supervision.  Conditions of probation are:
1) Maintain absolute sobriety;
2) Maintain full-time employment, schooling or combination; 
3) Assessment/treatment/counseling as deemed appropriate by the Department's assessment process;
4) Provide DNA sampe and pay for surcharge;
5) Pay restitution of $1,363.00 to the City of Manitowoc;
6) Pay costs of action;
7) Pay supervision fees in an amount to be determined by DOC.  
Court finds the defendant is not eligible for the Challenge Incarceration Program or the Substance Abuse Program.   
Defendant is given credit for 325 days served.   
